trans-unit.source: Provides data for the **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** event.
trans-unit.target: Proporciona datos para el evento **AnonymousIdentification_Creating**.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Esta clase no puede heredarse.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationEventArgs> class is used to supply event values to the <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule.Creating> event and to enable you to specify a custom Windows identity for the current request.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationEventArgs> clase se utiliza para proporcionar valores de evento para el <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule.Creating> eventos y que le permite especificar una identidad de Windows personalizada para la solicitud actual.

trans-unit.source: You can access the <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule.Creating> event of the <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule> class by specifying a subroutine named **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** in the Global.asax file for your ASP.NET application.
trans-unit.target: Puede tener acceso a la <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule.Creating> eventos de la <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule> clase especificando una subrutina denominada **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** en el archivo Global.asax de la aplicación ASP.NET.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule> constructs a <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationEventArgs> object using the current <xref:System.Web.HttpContext> and passes it to the **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** event.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule> construye una <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationEventArgs> uso actual del objeto <xref:System.Web.HttpContext> y lo pasa a la **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** eventos.

trans-unit.source: You can use the <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationEventArgs.AnonymousID%2A> property of the <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationEventArgs> object supplied to the **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** event to set the anonymous identifier to a custom value.
trans-unit.target: Puede usar el <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationEventArgs.AnonymousID%2A> propiedad de la <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationEventArgs> objeto proporcionado a la **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** eventos para establecer el identificador anónimo en un valor personalizado.

trans-unit.source: If you do not specify a value for the <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationEventArgs.AnonymousID%2A> property during the **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** event, a <xref:System.Guid> is used.
trans-unit.target: Si no especifica un valor para el <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationEventArgs.AnonymousID%2A> propiedad durante la **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** eventos, un <xref:System.Guid> se utiliza.

trans-unit.source: The **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** event is only raised when the anonymous identification is <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule.Enabled%2A>.
trans-unit.target: El **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** evento solo se genera cuando la identificación anónima es <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule.Enabled%2A>.

trans-unit.target: El siguiente ejemplo de código utiliza el **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** eventos para establecer el identificador anónimo en un valor personalizado.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule> constructs a <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationEventArgs> object using the current <xref:System.Web.HttpContext>.

trans-unit.source: It then passes the <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationEventArgs> object to the **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** event.
trans-unit.target: A continuación, pasa el <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationEventArgs> el objeto a la **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** eventos.

trans-unit.target: Obtiene o establece el identificador anónimo del usuario.

trans-unit.target: Identificador anónimo del usuario.

trans-unit.target: Puede usar el <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationEventArgs.AnonymousID%2A> propiedad para establecer el identificador anónimo en un valor personalizado durante el **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** eventos.

trans-unit.source: If you do not specify a value for the <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationEventArgs.AnonymousID%2A> property during the **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** event, a <xref:System.Guid> is used.
trans-unit.target: Si no especifica un valor para el <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationEventArgs.AnonymousID%2A> propiedad durante la **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** eventos, un <xref:System.Guid> se utiliza.

trans-unit.source: The **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** event is only raised when the anonymous identification is <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule.Enabled%2A>.
trans-unit.target: El **AnonymousIdentification_Creating** evento solo se genera cuando la identificación anónima es <xref:System.Web.Security.AnonymousIdentificationModule.Enabled%2A>.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <see cref="T:System.Web.HttpContext" /> object for the current HTTP request.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene el objeto <see cref="T:System.Web.HttpContext" /> de la solicitud HTTP actual.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.HttpContext" /> object for the current HTTP request.
trans-unit.target: Objeto <see cref="T:System.Web.HttpContext" /> de la solicitud HTTP actual.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.HttpContext> provides access to <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.Request%2A>, <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.Response%2A>, and <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.User%2A> objects for the current request.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.HttpContext> proporciona acceso a <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.Request%2A>, <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.Response%2A>, y <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.User%2A> objetos para la solicitud actual.
